data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER SAYS BRING AN OFFER! Ideal location, great floorplan, & thoughtful updates!! Prime spot in Crown Point close to both schools & downtown is this 3 bed, 2.5 bath, 1.5 story home. Welcoming, covered front porch leads into formal dining or living room w/ vaulted ceilings & tons of natural light flowing in. Open concept kitchen & rec room flow together w/ easy access to deck for outdoor entertaining & grilling. MAIN FLOOR primary bedroom w/ ensuite. Upstairs you will find two spacious bedrooms, loft area, & full bath. Main floor laundry room. Basement is unfinished w/ tons of potential for additional living space or storage. Home is LOADED w/ UPDATES including roof (2021), HVAC (2021), dishwasher & microwave (2023), kitchen countertops (2023), front door & patio door (2023), fresh paint, new flooring, & staircase remodel (2023). Hardwired wifi boosters throughout & security cameras to stay. Spacious backyard & no neighbors!
